程序包 xyz.fsgik.common.bean

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    FsBean
    Bean info of object, usually resolved by FsBeanResolver.
    FsBeanCopier
    Bean properties copier for FsBean, to copy properties from source object to dest object.
    FsBeanResolver
    Resolver for FsBean, usually consists of FsBeanResolver.Handlers.
    FsBeanResolver.Handler
    Handler of FsBeanResolver.
    FsBeanResolver.ResolveContext
    Context of bean resolving.
    FsProperty
    Represents property of a bean (FsBean).
    FsPropertyBase
    Base info of property of a bean (FsBean).
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    FsBeanCopier.Builder
    Builder for FsBeanCopier.
  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    FsBeanException
    Exception for bean.
